♬ the sound and
in and out the valley

281
00:22:29,947 --> 00:22:37,287
♬～

282
00:22:37,287 --> 00:22:40,791
♬ The music dance and sing

283
00:22:40,791 --> 00:22:44,395
♬ They make
the children really ring

284
