♬ the sound and
in and out the valley

287
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:58,740
♬ In and around the lake

288
00:23:00,077 --> 00:23:04,077
♬ Mountains come out of
the sky and they stand there

289
00:23:06,950 --> 00:23:10,550
♬ One mile over we'll be there
and we'll see you

290
00:23:13,590 --> 00:23:15,092
♬ Ten true summers

291
00:23:15,092 --> 00:23:17,192
♬ we'll be there
and laughing too

292
